00:36:23,086 --> 00:36:25,326
A ripe banana peel
will still make people fall.

544
00:36:34,286 --> 00:36:36,206
I still can't pass this damn level.

545
00:36:37,806 --> 00:36:39,606
Qinghe, are you okay?

