589
00:38:54,446 --> 00:38:55,646
Thanks for your concern.

590
00:39:00,286 --> 00:39:01,406
Shancai, read this.

591
00:39:04,646 --> 00:39:07,846
"Freshmen Chen Qinghe and Dong Shancai
received the Joker,

592
00:39:07,926 --> 00:39:09,446
